Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_disable...quential_cells(25.10)  timing_disable...quential_cells(25.10)

Name
       timing_disable_constant_propagation_for_sequential_cells

Syntax
       timing_disable_constant_propagation_for_sequential_cells

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Controls constant propagation across sequential cells.

       When set to true, the software disables constant propagation across se-
       quential cells.

       When set to false, the software enables constant propagation across se-
       quential cells.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

